    "answer": "1",
    "hint": "Cross-multiply, collect terms with \\(x\\) on one side, then factor.",
    "solution": "\\(y(cx + d) = ax + b\\) \\(\\Rightarrow\\) \\(cxy - ax = b - dy\\) \\(\\Rightarrow\\) \\(x(cy - a) = b - dy\\) \\(\\Rightarrow\\) \\(x = \\dfrac{dy - b}{a - cy}\\).",
